            ],
            "stanza_text": "Non. Pas assez chaud. Que notre âme\nRenaisse, prenne un bain de flamme"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "O Zéphyr, tandis que tu bouges",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Que toutes les lèvres soient rouges",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "O Zéphyr, tandis que tu bouges\nQue toutes les lèvres soient rouges"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Que hors du corsage, sans honte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Tressaillent, sans rendre nul compte",
